title: Creates a temporary commission on eminent domain; appropriation
summary: Creates a temporary commission on eminent domain reform to examine, evaluate and make recommendations concerning the scope and effectiveness of eminent domain procedure laws and the use of such power by public entities; makes a $100,000 appropriation to fund such temporary commission.
actClause: AN ACT to provide for the creation of a temporary state commission to examine eminent domain laws and make recommendations for further reforms; and making an appropriation therefor
